dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights on Edinburgh map. Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights on Scotland map. Depths shown by gradient tints on Scotland map. Edinburgh map shows county boundaries, boundaries with England, roads, highways, railways, parks, golf courses, cemeteries, and tourist points of interest. Scotland map shows roads, highways, railways, ferry lines with travel times, airports, golf courses, national parks, and tourist points of interest. Includes indexes and inset map of Shetland Islands. "© ITMB Publishing, 2nd edition 2013". Panel title.
